trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement> class uses classes derived from DiscoveryEndpointProvider to get the discovery endpoint to use.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement>klassen brukes klasser som er avledet fra DiscoveryEndpointProvider til å hente endepunktoppdagelse skal brukes.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryEndpointProvider"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryEndpointProvider"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement> class calls the GetDiscoveryEndpoint method on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryEndpointProvider> instance passed by the user to get the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryEndpoint> for discovering the services.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement>klassen kaller GetDiscoveryEndpoint-metoden på den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryEndpointProvider>forekomsten sendt av brukeren for å få den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryEndpoint>for å oppdage tjenestene.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryEndpoint> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryEndpointProvider> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement> also calls GetDiscoveryEndpoint method whenever it must clone itself.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement>kaller GetDiscoveryEndpoint metoden også når den må klone seg selv.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement>
